/p></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r1700" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-sm-12"><a href="/"  title="" aria-label="" class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m2392" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="P.A. Searle - Professional Tree Surgeons in Surrey and Hampshire" data-author="" width="171" height="170" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/WUK7AFGk/171x0_171x0/logo__ms__msi___jpg.webp" data-lazyload-id="m2392" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="P.A. Searle - Professional Tree Surgeons in Surrey and Hampshire" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=none,hovertransition=slowFadeIn"> <img id="m2392" class="module image" src="/uploads/WUK7AFGk/171x0_171x0/logo__ms__msi___jpg.webp" alt="P.A. Searle - Professional Tree Surgeons in Surrey and Hampshire" width="171" height="170" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> </div> <div class="col col col-sm-9 hidden-sm flexCol"><div id="m2454" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <div id="m2782" class="module text"><p class="custom2">Providing Expert Tree Services since 1980&nbsp;<span class="iconfont"></span><span class="iconfont"></span></p></div> <div id="m4732" class="module text"><p class="custom3"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Contact Us</span> Now to Discuss Our Services</p></div> <div id="m2649" class="module text"><p class="custom4"><span class="iconfont "></span>&nbsp;01276 471586&nbsp; |&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="redactor-invisible-space"><span class="iconfont "></span>&nbsp;</span>07966 195059</p></div> </div> <div id="m3568" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r5000" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c4354" class="col col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><nav id="m5000" class="module nav" data-settings="vertical=false,direction=right,push=true,activeParent=false" tabindex="-1"> <ul class="navContainer"><li class=" active"> <a href="/" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Home</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/tree-services-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Tree Services</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/stump-grinding-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Stump Grinding</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/testimonials-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Testimonials</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/gallery-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Gallery</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/about-us-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">About Us</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/blogs" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Blogs</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/contact-us-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact Us</a> </li><li class=""> <a href="/important-information" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Important Information</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/thank-you" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Thank You</a> </li><li class=" hidden-lg hidden-md hidden-sm"> <a href="/privacy-policy" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Privacy Policy</a> </li></ul> </nav></div> </div> </div> </header><div id="r5002" role="main" class="row designRow"> <div class="container container-fluid"><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="r2802" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-sm-12 flexCol"><div id="m1656" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="r1265" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m4563" class="module text"><h1 class="spottext"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Reliable Tree Surgery</span> Services in Surrey and Hampshire</h1></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div id="c1548" class="col col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-sm-12 flexCol"><div class="flexWrap"> <div class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m3346"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="approved tree doctor" data-author="" width="800" height="451" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/ntDRqaXv/768x0_640x0/rsz_lumberjack_in_a_black_shirt_sawing_a_chainsaw_on_mango_tree_650__ms__msi___jpg.webp" data-lazyload-id="m3346" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="approved tree doctor" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=none,hovertransition=slowFadeIn"> <img id="m3346" class="module image" src="/uploads/ntDRqaXv/768x0_640x0/rsz_lumberjack_in_a_black_shirt_sawing_a_chainsaw_on_mango_tree_650__ms__msi___jpg.webp" alt="approved tree doctor" width="800" height="451" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </div><div id="m3843" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle">Approved Tree Surgeons</h2></div> <div id="m1057" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">P.A. Searle is a trusted company specialising in <a href="/tree-services-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">expert tree surgery services.</a> Our team of highly qualified tree surgeons serves Surrey and Hampshire with extensive industry training and experience. We cater to both domestic and commercial clients, offering a comprehensive range of services including tree removal, hedge trimming, and more. Our priority is to safeguard and enhance your property with professional care and attention to detail. <a href="/contact-us-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact us</a> today to discover how P.A. Searle can assist you with your tree surgery needs.</p></div> </div> <div id="m1160" class="module autospacer"></div> <div class="flexWrap"> <a id="m3281" class="module button" href="/tree-services-surrey"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <i class="buttonIcon fa fa-chevron-circle-right "></i> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Tree Services</span> </a></div> </div> <div class="col col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-sm-12"> <div class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m3051"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="stump left after tree fell in farnborough" data-author="" width="800" height="451" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/hvCw2iJn/768x0_640x0/rsz_shutterstock_102813929_623__ms__msi___jpg.webp" data-lazyload-id="m3051" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="stump left after tree fell in farnborough" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=none,hovertransition=slowFadeIn"> <img id="m3051" class="module image" src="/uploads/hvCw2iJn/768x0_640x0/rsz_shutterstock_102813929_623__ms__msi___jpg.webp" alt="stump left after tree fell in farnborough" width="800" height="451" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </div><div id="m4542" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle">Removing Problem Stumps</h2></div> <div id="m4356" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Problematic tree stumps can quickly become not just inconvenient but also hazardous if left unaddressed. To effectively eliminate stumps from your property, <a href="/stump-grinding-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">stump grinding</a> stands out as the most efficient solution available. Our dedicated tree surgery services specialise in addressing such challenges, ensuring your property remains safe and visually appealing. With our expertise and commitment to quality, we provide reliable and friendly customer service, always available to assist you with any tree-related concerns. Whether you need stump removal, tree pruning, or extensive tree care, our team is here to help you maintain a healthy and beautiful outdoor environment.</p></div> <a id="m4327" class="module button" href="/stump-grinding-surrey"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <i class="buttonIcon fa fa-chevron-circle-right "></i> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Stump Grinding</span> </a></div> </div> </div> <div id="r4619" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div class="col col-sm-12"><div id="m4058" class="module text"><h3 class="preamble"><a href="/contact-us-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Get in touch</a> with the tree surgery experts at P.A. Searle today, for more information on<br>our range of professional tree services, THE BEST OPTIONS FOR YOU or for a non-obligatory quote to find out more about our competitive prices, contact our FRIENDLY team today on <a data-global="phone"  href="tel:01276471586" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="phone_link">01276 471586</a>.</h3></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-sm-12"><div id="m1100" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle">About Us</h2></div> <div id="m1107" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">If you’re a home or business owner looking for a professional and reliable tree surgery company in Frimley, Farnborough, Camberley, Lightwater, or the wider Surrey and Hampshire areas, look no further than P.A. Searle. Based in Bagshot, our local tree surgeons are qualified and experienced in managing all areas of tree work and grounds maintenance. Whether you require <a href="/tree-services-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">tree removal services</a>, regular hedge cutting or one-off <a href="/stump-grinding-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">stump grinding</a> at your property, we are able to shape gardens while preserving their health.</p></div> <div id="m4625" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">At P.A. Searle we know how important it is to have your trees in the best condition possible. Whether your need for tree care stems from environmental considerations, aesthetic preferences, or safety concerns, we are the dependable tree surgery company you can trust. We have over eighty years of experience when it comes to tree surgery, so you can have peace of mind, with the knowledge that you’re receiving the highest-quality service. We have completed a diverse array of <a href="/gallery-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">projects</a>, ensuring that we approach every task with equal dedication and expertise, regardless of its scale.</p></div> <a id="m3602" class="module button" href="/gallery-surrey"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <i class="buttonIcon fa fa-chevron-circle-right "></i> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">View Our Gallery</span> </a></div> <div class="col col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-sm-12"><div id="m1039" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle">Services We Provide</h2></div> <div id="m1581" class="module text"><p class="bodytext">Serving clients throughout Surrey and Hampshire, we provide a wide <a href="/tree-services-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">variety of services</a>, including:</p></div> <div id="m1740" class="module list" data-settings=""> <p class="headline listTitle">Services we provide</p> <ul> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Tree Felling </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Tree and Hedge Shaping </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Stump Grinding </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Hedge Cutting and Formative Pruning </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Safe and Ethical Deadwood Removal </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Crown Reduction, Thinning and Lifting </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> </ul> </div></div> </div> </div> <div id="r2219" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed "><div id="c3135" class="col col-lg-6 col-sm-5 hidden-sm flexCol"><div id="m3885" class="module autospacer"></div> </div> <div class="col col-lg-6 col-md-7 col-sm-12"> <div class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m2379"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="A tree with overhanging branches removed" data-author="" width="800" height="450" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/IT5VYsvx/768x0_640x0/deadPinecairnclose2_13__ms__msi___jpeg.webp" data-lazyload-id="m2379" data-lazyload-class="module image hidden-lg hidden-md" data-lazyload-alt="A tree with overhanging branches removed" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=none,hovertransition=slowFadeIn"> <img id="m2379" class="module image hidden-lg hidden-md" src="/uploads/IT5VYsvx/768x0_640x0/deadPinecairnclose2_13__ms__msi___jpeg.webp" alt="A tree with overhanging branches removed" width="800" height="450" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </div><div id="m3633" class="module text"><h2 class="subtitle">Why P.A. Searle is the tree surgeon for you:</h2></div> <div id="m2423" class="module list" data-settings="listcols=1,margin=0"> <p class="headline listTitle">Why use us</p> <ul> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Free Advice and Quotes for Competitively Priced Services </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Hedge Cutting </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Managing Removals, including Felling and Stump Grinding </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> A Company Guarantee Covers Tree Surgery Services in Frimley, Farnborough, Camberley, Lightwater, and the Wider Surrey and Hampshire Counties </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Insured by up to £10 Million in Public and Employers Liability </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Adheres to BS 3998:2010 Tree Work – Recommendations </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Our Fully-Qualified Tree Surgeons </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> <li> <p class="bodytext listItem"> <span class="iconTextWrapper"> <span class="iconContainer"> <i class="listIcon fa fa-check" data-preferred></i> </span> <span class="bodytext itemLabel"> <span class="itemMainText"> Endorsed by Local Authorities throughout Surrey and Hampshire </span> </span> </span> </span> </p> </li> </ul> </div><div id="m2635" class="module text"><p class="bodytext"><a href="/contact-us-surrey" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked">Contact us today</a>, and our friendly, knowledgeable team will be more than happy to discuss options that may be more suitable to your personal tree surgery needs, we are here to help!&nbsp;</p></div> <a id="m1641" class="module button" href="/testimonials-surrey"  title="" role="button" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="internal_link_clicked"> <i class="buttonIcon fa fa-chevron-circle-right "></i> <span class="buttonLabel labelRight">Read Our Reviews</span> </a></div> </div> </div> <div id="r3146" class="row row hidden-lg hidden-md"> <div class="container container-fixed "><div class="col col-sm-12"><a href="https://trustedtraders.which.co.uk/businesses/p-a-searle/"  title="Check out our reviews on Which? Trusted Trader" class="imageModuleWrap" id="w_m2748" data-track-event="click" data-track-action="link_clicked"> <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAAC0lEQVQYV2NgAAIAAAUAAarVyFEAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="Which? Trusted Trader" data-author="" width="1179" height="934" fetchpriority="high"/> <noscript data-lazyload-src="/uploads/gUs3svpW/480x0_1179x0/WhichTrustedTraderLogo__ms__msi___JPG.webp" data-lazyload-id="m2748" data-lazyload-class="module image" data-lazyload-alt="Which? Trusted Trader" data-req="" data-settings="enablehover=false,showelement=,hovertransition="> <img id="m2748" class="module image" src="/uploads/gUs3svpW/480x0_1179x0/WhichTrustedTraderLogo__ms__msi___JPG.webp" alt="Which? Trusted Trader" width="1179" height="934" data-author="" fetchpriority="high"/> </noscript> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <footer><div id="r1074" class="row "> <div class="container container-fixed"><div class="col col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-lg-3"><div id="m1028" class="module text"><p class="custom1"><span class="redactor-invisible-space"><span class="iconfont"></span>&nbsp;</span>P.A. Searle</p></div> <div id="m4255" class="module text"><p class="footertext">85 College Ride</p><p class="footertext">Bagshot</p><p class="footertext">Surrey</p><p class="footertext">GU19 5EP</p></div> <div id="m4637" class="module text"><p class="footertext">VAT Reg No.&nbsp;358 7934</p></div> </div> <div id="c1577" class="col col-md-3 col-sm-12 col-lg-3"><div id="m1014" class="module text"><p class="custom1"><span class="iconfont"></span>&nbsp;Get In Touch